OL,3,C'Thoroughly evil' man jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering partner
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced to life in
OL,7,Fprison for murdering his girlfriend on
OL,8,Fthe night she planned to end their
OL,9,Frelationship.
OL,11,FKieron Goodwin, 33, has been sentenced
OL,12,Fto life imprisonment with a minimum
OL,13,Fterm of 35 years for the murder of his
OL,14,Fpartner Olivia Wood, 29, who he
OL,15,Fstrangled in July last year.
OL,17,FBristol Crown Court heard that Goodwin
OL,18,Fkilled Ms Wood in Frome on the night
OL,19,Fshe planned to end their relationship,
OL,20,Fwhich had lasted less than three
OL,21,Fmonths.
