OL,3,C'Thoroughly evil' man jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering partner
OL,6,FPolice discovered packed suitcases and
OL,7,Fbags filled with her belongings at his
OL,8,Fflat, indicating her intention to
OL,9,Fleave.
OL,11,FGoodwin, who denied the murder but was
OL,12,Fconvicted following a five-week trial,
OL,13,Fwas also found guilty of 15 additional
OL,14,Foffences against Ms Wood and three
OL,15,Fother women.
OL,17,FThe offences included rape, assault by
OL,18,Fpenetration, intentional strangulation
OL,19,Fand causing a person to engage in
OL,20,Fsexual activity without consent.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
