OL,3,C'Thoroughly evil' man jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering partner
OL,6,FJudge Martin Picton imposed nine
OL,7,Fconcurrent life sentences for the
OL,8,Fsexual offences alongside the murder
OL,9,Fconviction, describing Goodwin as "a
OL,10,Fhighly manipulative, deviant
OL,11,Fmisogynist and selfish narcissist" who
OL,12,Fwas "thoroughly evil".
OL,14,FThe court was told Goodwin had
OL,15,Fsubjected Ms Wood to physical and
OL,16,Fpsychological abuse, forcing her to
OL,17,Ftake time off work through threats of
OL,18,Fself-harm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
