OL,3,C'Thoroughly evil' man jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering partner
OL,6,FHe also pressured her into
OL,7,Ftransferring more than #6,000 to help
OL,8,Fpay bills, which he instead spent on
OL,9,Fcocaine.
OL,11,FGoodwin admitted to controlling and
OL,12,Fcoercive behaviour against all his
OL,13,Fvictims, but denied the other
OL,14,Foffences, claiming the women had
OL,15,Fconsented to the sexual activity.
OL,17,FThe jury was told Goodwin used to ply
OL,18,Fthe women with drugs, threaten to send
OL,19,Fcompromising photos to friends, family
OL,20,For work colleagues and report them to
OL,21,Fthe police.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
