OL,3,C'Thoroughly evil' man jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering partner
OL,6,FHe made them hand over tens of
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds which he used to
OL,8,Ffund his cocaine habit and lifestyle
OL,9,Fwhile also threatening to harm himself
OL,10,Fif anyone rejected him in any way.
OL,12,FAt 2.50am on Tuesday 30 July 2024,
OL,13,FGoodwin made a 999 call to the
OL,14,Fambulance service reporting that
OL,15,FOlivia was not breathing, and she was
OL,16,Ftaken to hospital where she later died.
OL,18,F'Her loss has left a hole in her
OL,19,Ffamily that will never be filled'
