OL,3,C'Thoroughly evil' man jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering partner
OL,6,F"I miss her voice, her laugh, her
OL,7,Fwarmth, her stories from work, her
OL,8,Fexperiences with the little animals
OL,9,Fthat she loved so much. There was
OL,10,Falways a beetle or a bumblebee to
OL,11,Frescue."
OL,13,FDetective Superintendent Lorett
OL,14,FSpierenburg, the senior investigating
OL,15,Fofficer, said: "We know how special
OL,16,FOlivia was - her kindness and
OL,17,Fcompassion for others, not only
OL,18,Fpeople, but also for wildlife has
OL,19,Fbecome so clearly evident over these
OL,20,Fpast nine months.
