OL,3,C'Thoroughly evil' man jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering partner
OL,6,F"Her loss has left a hole in her
OL,7,Ffamily that will never be filled.
OL,8,FDespite that, they have had to sit in
OL,9,Fcourt for more than a month while
OL,10,FGoodwin refused to admit to her murder
OL,11,Fand refused to give them the answers
OL,12,Fthey deserve.
OL,14,F"Not only did he manipulate and abuse
OL,15,FOlivia, but he did the same to the
OL,16,Fvictims whose courage in coming
OL,17,Fforward and reporting his crimes
OL,18,Fagainst them has undoubtedly protected
OL,19,Fother women.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
