OL,6,F"Each of them deserves far more credit
OL,7,Fthan I could ever possibly give them,
OL,8,Fbut they should be so proud of
OL,9,Fthemselves and how they have not only
OL,10,Fstood up against Goodwin but also
OL,11,Fstood up for women everywhere."
